FBIS3-48368 "dreas016_c_94033" FBIS-EAS-94-016 Document Type:Daily Report 25 Jan 1994 North Korea Foreign Minister Greets Zambian Counterpart SK2001114194 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1034 GMT 20 Jan 94 SK2001114194 Pyongyang KCNA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Pyongyang, January 20 (KCNA) -- Foreign Minister Kim Yong-nam sent a message of greetings to Remmy K.K.G. Mushota on his appointment as foreign minister of the Republic of Zambia. Expressing the belief that the friendly and cooperative relations between the two countries would develop more favorably, the message wholeheartedly wished him great success in his responsible work.
